==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nightly
<hw>Night"ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to the night, or
to every night; happening or done by night, or every night; <as>as,
<ex>nightly</ex> shades; he kept <ex>nightly</ex> vigils.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nightly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Nightly
<hw>Night"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>At night; every night.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nightman</ent>⟦br⟧
